{"tid":1415330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"投擲投巧有需要加強","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T12:05:37.000Z","uid":281067,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e05688f81144a2ffdb40198fc3af9fc2c817016e","tid":1415330,"uid":281067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:33:30.000Z","msg":"本人連登新人，棒球撚一個，覺得大家投擲技巧需要加強。寫左少少雞精文幫幫大家，投要投好少少，俾d精神。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hydejing.pixnet.net/blog/post/31092835-%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%A8%99%E6%BA%96%E5%A7%BF%E5%8B%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhydejing.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F31092835-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2588%25AC%25E6%25A8%2599%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%25A7%25BF%25E5%258B%25A2&d=m%2FvCTr80Ma3Q2SiS6jp77ckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=58fdc56f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hydejing.pixnet.net/blog/post/31092835-%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%A8%99%E6%BA%96%E5%A7%BF%E5%8B%A2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y8f0JAz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY8f0JAz.jpg&h=137d31c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無野揸個邊手指向目標<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dALoGpU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdALoGpU.jpg&h=c79246e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無野揸個邊手扭動，至手背貼心口<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qjAjZbX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqjAjZbX.jpg&h=55af3860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重心腳踩實，踏前一步<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ujOUN5K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FujOUN5K.jpg&h=d4e2e05a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n揸野手要過頭，用力，fing出好似一條鞭禁，指向目標，放，手自然落下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZ5ggZT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZ5ggZT.jpg&h=b4ae7e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9eus76Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9eus76Z.jpg&h=8b296b60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GxZ1vVy_b10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGxZ1vVy_b10&d=m%2FvCTr80Ma3Q2SiS6jp77ckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=5bb5d92d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GxZ1vVy_b10</a>"},{"pid":"423c11c55887955417c2a312ccf8d5dde4a60c30","tid":1415330,"uid":281067,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"954d6883d8a38ad07654f06b21abf9434b73bb42","tid":1415330,"uid":281067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:35:18.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"65c3dac80106f89f54f4ff30bac98e0740c89681","tid":1415330,"uid":281067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"fc0120157327d5efbadbdcf5bc57fa87bbb481a4","tid":1415330,"uid":281067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"有人補充：<br />\n記住投球嗰陣手肘要高過膊頭<br />\n如果唔係好易傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e457e83877c4e0a15fd8e73a02038fd1f2fa79","tid":1415330,"uid":281067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:40:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4652f418b682f0ea7addd4e5bc81676692aae6c8","tid":1415330,"uid":281067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:40:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e83d9616a9cfa4f298693ab20063bdcebc906d5a","tid":1415330,"uid":281067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:40:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5f9784b2dfbde5429a26cf1464c4563f0fb986a","tid":1415330,"uid":281067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:40:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"213a95e7864dd730bcfa7d6baefc9bb520279ebb","tid":1415330,"uid":281067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:40:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8554e8361010c14add9b2d3fd4d3630ff8b4731","tid":1415330,"uid":48836